[10/02/2018 02:13:17] <font color="#ffffff">sino a los estudios.</font>
[10/02/2018 02:13:20] <font color="#ffffff">(SILBA)</font>
[10/02/2018 02:13:22] <font color="#0000ff">(Bocinas)</font>
