[10/02/2018 22:52:49] <font color="#00ff00">Otra de las candidatas maravillosas,</font>
[10/02/2018 22:52:49] <font color="#00ff00">Verónica Delgado.</font>
[10/02/2018 22:52:54] <font color="#00ff00">Maravillosa fantasía,</font>
[10/02/2018 22:52:54] <font color="#00ff00">diseñada por Daniel Baute.</font>
[10/02/2018 22:52:57] <font color="#00ff00">Maravillosa, "Luna Blanca",</font>
[10/02/2018 22:53:02] <font color="#00ff00">de Quintero.</font>
[10/02/2018 22:53:08] <font color="#00ff00">Es de la comparsa Río Orinoco.</font>
